sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as User/Client
    participant Gateway as data-science-gateway<br/>(Envoy)<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant MLflow as MLflow Server<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS<br/>(service-ca TLS)
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS
    participant DB as Backend Database<br/>(PostgreSQL 5432/TCP<br/>or MySQL 3306/TCP)
    participant S3 as Artifact Storage<br/>(S3/MinIO/SeaweedFS)<br/>443/9000/8333 TCP

    Note over Client,S3: Flow 1: User Access to MLflow via Gateway API

    Client->>Gateway: POST /mlflow/api/*<br/>HTTPS TLS 1.2+<br/>Auth: Bearer Token (K8s SA token)
    Gateway->>MLflow: Forward to /api/*<br/>HTTPS TLS (service-ca)<br/>Forwarded Bearer Token
    MLflow->>K8sAPI: SelfSubjectAccessReview<br/>HTTPS TLS 1.2+<br/>Auth: Service Account Token
    K8sAPI-->>MLflow: RBAC Decision (allow/deny)
    MLflow->>DB: Query/Store metadata<br/>TLS (configurable)<br/>Auth: DB credentials
    DB-->>MLflow: Query Results
    MLflow->>S3: Store/Retrieve artifacts<br/>HTTPS TLS<br/>Auth: AWS IAM credentials
    S3-->>MLflow: Artifact Data
    MLflow-->>Gateway: API Response
    Gateway-->>Client: JSON Response

    Note over Client,S3: Flow 2: Operator Reconciliation

    participant Operator as MLflow Operator<br/>Controller Manager

    Operator->>K8sAPI: Watch MLflow CRs<br/>HTTPS TLS 1.2+<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
    K8sAPI-->>Operator: MLflow CR Event
    Note over Operator: Helm template rendering<br/>(internal, no network)
    Operator->>K8sAPI: Server-Side Apply<br/>(Deployment, Service, NetworkPolicy,<br/>PVC, RBAC, HTTPRoute, ConsoleLink)<br/>HTTPS TLS 1.2+<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
    K8sAPI-->>Operator: Apply Result

    Note over Client,S3: Flow 3: Prometheus Metrics Scraping

    participant Prom as Prometheus

    Prom->>MLflow: GET /metrics<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS<br/>TLS (service-ca)<br/>Auth: None (ServiceMonitor)
    MLflow-->>Prom: Prometheus Metrics
